OL,3,CFresh appeal three years after drive-
OL,4,Cby shooting at car wash
OL,6,FThree years after a man died in a
OL,7,Fdrive-by shooting at a car wash,
OL,8,Fpolice have renewed their appeal for
OL,9,Finformation to find those responsible
OL,10,Ffor his death.
OL,12,FLamar Leroy Griffiths, 21, was killed
OL,13,Fon 29 March, 2022 when shots were
OL,14,Ffired at the car he was sitting in at
OL,15,FDiamond Hand Car Wash, in Burngreave,
OL,16,FSheffield.
OL,18,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the people
OL,19,Fresponsible for Mr Griffiths's murder
OL,20,Fwere "yet to be brought to justice".
