OL,3,CFresh appeal three years after drive-
OL,4,Cby shooting at car wash
OL,6,FDet Insp David Robertson said: "A
OL,7,Fnumber of extensive and comprehensive
OL,8,Finquiries have been made into this
OL,9,Fhorrific crime which tragically cut
OL,10,Fshort Lamar's life in the most brutal
OL,11,Fof circumstances.
OL,13,F"Lamar's injuries proved fatal and he
OL,14,Fdied at the scene, with our
OL,15,Finvestigation since leading us to
OL,16,Fbelieve that he was not the intended
OL,17,Ftarget of this attack.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
