OL,3,CFresh appeal three years after drive-
OL,4,Cby shooting at car wash
OL,6,F"We will continue to pursue every line
OL,7,Fof inquiry we receive in relation to
OL,8,Fthis case and I would urge members of
OL,9,Fthe public who have relevant
OL,10,Finformation to please contact us
OL,11,Fimmediately."
OL,13,FIn June last year, two men were jailed
OL,14,Fafter they pleaded guilty to assisting
OL,15,Fan offender in connection with the
OL,16,Fshooting.
