OL,6,FAt the time of their conviction, a
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid Abdul Hakim and Nasser Nashir
OL,9,Fdestroyed evidence and helped two
OL,10,Fmurder suspects escape justice.
OL,12,FHakim was jailed for seven years and
OL,13,Feight months at Sheffield Crown Court,
OL,14,Fwith Nashir imprisoned for five years.
