OL,3,CFresh appeal three years after drive-
OL,4,Cby shooting at car wash
OL,6,FDet Insp Robertson said: "The
OL,7,Finvestigation into Lamar's death is
OL,8,Fcontinuing and, following the
OL,9,Fsentencing of Hakim and Nashir, we
OL,10,Fhave continued to do everything within
OL,11,Four power to bring the people they
OL,12,Fhelped before the UK courts.
OL,14,F"If you saw what happened and haven't
OL,15,Fyet contacted police then I implore
OL,16,Fyou to do so for Lamar and his loved
OL,17,Fones.
